SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1 t , :2 c , :3 b where t.tr_boekdatum between ~4 and ~5 and t.tr_transnummer > 0 and c.cl_nummer = t.tr_rel2 and c.cl_boek_categorie in (:6) and b.be_symbool = t.tr_symbool and b.be_optietype = t.tr_optietype and b.be_expiratiedatum = t.tr_expiratiedatum and b.be_exerciseprijs = t.tr_exerciseprijs and b.be_bi_nummer in (:7) and t.tr_indicatie in (:8)
